---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Area Soci — NexLudica APS" description="Area riservata agli associati NexLudica: gestione profilo, upload resoconti MeetLudica, materiali interni.">
  <section class="bg-nx-off-white px-4 pb-12 pt-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-nx-cyan">Riservato</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-nx-dark sm:text-6xl" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
        Area Soci
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-nx-gray-dark">
        L'area riservata ai soci di NexLudica. Da qui puoi gestire il tuo profilo,
        caricare documenti per la community e accedere ai materiali interni.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Banner stato MVP -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 pt-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-5 text-sm text-amber-900">
      <p class="font-semibold">🚧 Area in costruzione</p>
      <p class="mt-1">
        Le interfacce qui sotto sono pronte ma il backend di autenticazione e di archiviazione
        documenti non è ancora collegato. Per ora i form non salvano nulla. Sotto trovi le
        opzioni tecniche per attivare la versione "vera".
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tab content -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[280px_1fr]">
      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="space-y-1">
        <p class="px-3 pb-2 pt-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-nx-gray-dark">Account</p>
        <a href="#login" class="block rounded-md bg-nx-cyan-light px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-nx-cyan no-underline">
          Accedi
        </a>
        <a href="#profilo" class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark no-underline hover:bg-nx-off-white">
          Il mio profilo
        </a>

        <p class="mt-4 px-3 pb-2 pt-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-nx-gray-dark">MeetLudica</p>
        <a href="#upload-meetludica" class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark no-underline hover:bg-nx-off-white">
          Carica un resoconto
        </a>
        <a href="#i-miei-articoli" class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark no-underline hover:bg-nx-off-white">
          I miei articoli
        </a>
      </aside>

      <!-- Main content -->
      <main class="space-y-12">
        <!-- LOGIN -->
        <section id="login">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nx-dark">Accedi</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark">Inserisci le credenziali del tuo account socio.</p>

          <form class="mt-6 space-y-4 rounded-xl border border-nx-gray-light/20 bg-white p-6">
            <div>
              <label for="login-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Email</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="login-email"
                name="email"
                required
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="login-password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Password</label>
              <input
                type="password"
                id="login-password"
                name="password"
                required
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
              />
            </div>
            <button
              type="submit"
              disabled
              class="w-full rounded-lg bg-nx-cyan px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white opacity-60"
            >
              Accedi (auth non attiva)
            </button>
          </form>
        </section>

        <!-- UPLOAD RESOCONTO MEETLUDICA -->
        <section id="upload-meetludica">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nx-dark">Carica un resoconto MeetLudica</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark">
            Hai presentato a un MeetLudica? Pubblica qui il tuo resoconto: comparirà
            nell'archivio della pagina <a href="/meetludica" class="text-nx-cyan no-underline hover:underline">MeetLudica</a>.
          </p>

          <form class="mt-6 space-y-5 rounded-xl border border-nx-gray-light/20 bg-white p-6">
            <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <label for="article-title" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Titolo del talk</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="article-title"
                  name="title"
                  placeholder="es. Tabletop Science: gioco e ricerca"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="article-speaker" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Relatore/i</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="article-speaker"
                  name="speaker"
                  placeholder="Nome Cognome"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="article-date" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Data dell'incontro</label>
                <input
                  type="date"
                  id="article-date"
                  name="date"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <label for="article-tags" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Tag (separati da virgola)</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="article-tags"
                  name="tags"
                  placeholder="ricerca, design, NEET"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <label for="article-abstract" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Abstract</label>
                <textarea
                  id="article-abstract"
                  name="abstract"
                  rows="5"
                  placeholder="Breve sintesi del talk e dei principali spunti emersi nella discussione."
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <label for="article-pdf" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Documento (PDF)</label>
                <input
                  type="file"
                  id="article-pdf"
                  name="document"
                  accept="application/pdf"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-dashed border-nx-gray-light/40 bg-nx-off-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none file:mr-4 file:rounded-md file:border-0 file:bg-nx-cyan file:px-4 file:py-2 file:text-xs file:font-bold file:uppercase file:tracking-wider file:text-white"
                />
                <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-nx-gray-dark">Max 10 MB. Formato consigliato: PDF.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <label for="article-video" class="block text-sm font-medium text-nx-dark">Link registrazione (opzionale)</label>
                <input
                  type="url"
                  id="article-video"
                  name="videoUrl"
                  placeholder="https://"
                  class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-lg border border-nx-gray-light/40 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-nx-dark outline-none transition focus:border-nx-cyan focus:ring-2 focus:ring-nx-cyan/20"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <button
              type="submit"
              disabled
              class="rounded-lg bg-nx-cyan px-7 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white opacity-60"
            >
              Pubblica resoconto (storage non attivo)
            </button>
          </form>
        </section>

        <!-- I MIEI ARTICOLI -->
        <section id="i-miei-articoli">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nx-dark">I miei articoli</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-nx-gray-dark">
            Qui troverai i resoconti che hai pubblicato e potrai modificarli o eliminarli.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-dashed border-nx-gray-light/40 bg-nx-off-white p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-nx-gray-dark">Non hai ancora pubblicato resoconti.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Nota tecnica per Vittorio -->
  <section class="border-t border-nx-gray-light/20 bg-nx-off-white px-4 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-sm text-nx-gray-dark">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-nx-gray-dark">Nota tecnica</p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Per attivare upload e auth servono 3 risorse Cloudflare (gratuite per i volumi attesi):
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-nx-cyan"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-nx-dark">R2</strong> per archiviare i PDF dei resoconti.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-nx-cyan"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-nx-dark">D1</strong> (SQLite) per metadati articoli e utenti.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-nx-cyan"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-nx-dark">Cloudflare Access</strong> (o Auth0/Clerk) per il login dei soci.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
